{"surah":{"number":99,"name":"الزلزلة","englishName":"Az-Zalzalah","englishTranslation":"The Earthquake","ayahCount":8},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:55.574Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"When the earth is shaken with its [final] earthquake","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"When","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"زُلْزِلَتِ","english":"is shaken","translit":"zul'zilati","root":"زلزل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضُ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍu","root":"أرض"},{"position":4,"arabic":"زِلْزَالَهَا","english":"(with) its earthquake","translit":"zil'zālahā","root":"زلزل"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"And the earth discharges its burdens","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَخْرَجَتِ","english":"And brings forth","translit":"wa-akhrajati","root":"خرج"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضُ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍu","root":"أرض"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَثْقَالَهَا","english":"its burdens","translit":"athqālahā","root":"ثقل"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And man says, \"What is [wrong] with it?\" -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَقَالَ","english":"And says","translit":"waqāla","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ","english":"man","translit":"l-insānu","root":"أنس"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","english":"What","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَهَا","english":"(is) with it","translit":"lahā","root":""}]},{"number":4,"translation":"That Day, it will report its news","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"That Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"تُحَدِّثُ","english":"it will report","translit":"tuḥaddithu","root":"حدث"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَخْ